---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = 'No Surprises Act | Dr. Alan S. Lee, DDS - Manteca Dentist';
const description = 'Learn about your rights under the No Surprises Act, including Good Faith Estimates for dental services at Dr. Alan S. Lee, DDS in Manteca, CA.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>No Surprises Act</h1>
    <p>Your rights to a Good Faith Estimate and protection from unexpected bills</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="notice-box">
      <p><strong>Your Rights and Protections Against Surprise Medical Bills</strong></p>
      <p>Under the No Surprises Act, you have the right to receive a Good Faith Estimate for the expected charges for scheduled health care services.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>What Is the No Surprises Act?</h2>
    <p>The No Surprises Act is a federal law that provides protections against surprise medical bills. It went into effect on January 1, 2022, and gives you the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Receive a Good Faith Estimate of expected charges for scheduled services</li>
      <li>Dispute bills that are substantially higher than your Good Faith Estimate</li>
      <li>Be protected from surprise billing for emergency services</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Good Faith Estimates</h2>
    <p>Under the law, you have the right to receive a Good Faith Estimate for the total expected cost of any scheduled dental services. This includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Who qualifies:</strong> Anyone who is uninsured or who has insurance but is not using their insurance for a scheduled service</li>
      <li><strong>When to request:</strong> You can request a Good Faith Estimate at any time, including before you schedule a service</li>
      <li><strong>What it includes:</strong> The expected charges for the scheduled service, including any reasonably expected items or services</li>
      <li><strong>How to get one:</strong> Contact our office to request a Good Faith Estimate</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How to Request a Good Faith Estimate</h2>
    <p>To request a Good Faith Estimate, please contact our office:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+12092392990">(209) 239-2990</a></li>
      <li><strong>In person:</strong> 715 N Main St, Manteca, CA 95336</li>
      <li><strong>Online:</strong> <a href="/schedule-appointment/">Schedule an appointment</a> and request an estimate</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We will provide your Good Faith Estimate in writing within the timeframe required by law.</p>

    <h2>If Your Bill Exceeds Your Estimate</h2>
    <p>If you receive a bill that is at least $400 more than your Good Faith Estimate, you have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Dispute the charges</li>
      <li>Request a review of the dispute through an independent dispute resolution process</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For more information about your rights under the No Surprises Act, visit <a href="https://www.cms.gov/nosurprises" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.cms.gov/nosurprises</a>.</p>

    <h2>Our Commitment to Transparency</h2>
    <p>At the dental practice of Dr. Alan S. Lee, DDS, we are committed to transparent pricing and ensuring our patients understand the cost of their dental care. We will work with you to provide accurate estimates and discuss payment options before treatment begins.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights Under the No Surprises Act</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>You have the right to receive a Good Faith Estimate before scheduling services</li>
      <li>You have the right to be informed about the costs of your care before you receive it</li>
      <li>You have the right to dispute bills that are substantially higher than your estimate</li>
      <li>You have the right to receive a clear explanation of your bill</li>
      <li>You have the right to ask questions about your bill and your rights</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="cta-section">
      <h2>Questions About Your Estimate?</h2>
      <p>Contact our office and we'll be happy to help you understand your options.</p>
      <a href="tel:+12092392990" class="btn-cta-large">Call (209) 239-2990</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .notice-box { background: #e8f4fd; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .notice-box p { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .cta-section { text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; padding: 2rem; background: var(--bg-light); border-radius: 8px; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-family: var(--font-heading); color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .btn-cta-large { display: inline-block; background: var(--accent); color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-cta-large:hover { background: #d4952e; }
  </style>
</Layout>